{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01K7QkdQg4aFECxxFw14ZxtQ","type":"tool_result","content":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/archive/RNG_UTOPIA_OVERVIEW.md:- `MAX_FEE_BPS = 1000` (10% max, cannot exceed)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/archive/RNG_UTOPIA_OVERVIEW.md:    pub fee_bps: u16,           // Max 1000 (10%)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/archive/RNG_UTOPIA_QUICK_REF.md:├── fee_bps: u16 (max 1000 = 10%)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/archive/RNG_UTOPIA_QUICK_REF.md:Hard Limits: MAX_FEE = 10%, MAX_BET = 1000 SOL\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/history.md:- Added `ReferralEarning` interface (id, referrer_wallet, referee_wallet, round_id, game_type, wager_lamports, fee_lamports, referrer_earned_lamports, referrer_rate_bps, referee_rebate_lamports, referee_rebate_rate_bps, created_at)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/gap-analysis.md:| 3b | Rebate is exactly 1000 bps of fee_lamports (fixed, not configurable) | GAP | No calculation logic implemented |\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/gap-analysis.md:| 4b | Default referrer rate is 1000 bps of the total fee (configurable via environment/config) | GAP | No config env var `REFERRAL_DEFAULT_RATE_BPS` — grep in `config.ts` returns zero matches for \"referral\" |\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/gap-analysis.md:| 10c | KOL custom rate used when present, default otherwise | GAP | No rate lookup in settlement |\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:Referred players receive a **fixed 10% rebate on their own fees** (1000 bps of fee_lamports), accruing as a claimable SOL balance. This is permanent and not configurable — every referred player gets 10% back on every game, forever.\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:- [ ] Rebate is exactly 1000 bps of fee_lamports (fixed, not configurable) <!-- gap: no calculation logic implemented -->\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:- Default referrer share: **1000 bps of the total fee (= 50 bps of wager)**\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:- On a 1 SOL wager: total fee = 0.05 SOL (500 bps), referrer earns 0.005 SOL (1000 bps of the fee)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:- Platform revenue impact: 1000 bps (10%) haircut on fee revenue from referred players (referrer share only; referee reward is non-fee-based)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:**KOL override:** Admin can set a custom referrer rate per wallet (stored in DB). This supports partnership agreements where a KOL may receive a higher share (e.g., 2000-3000 bps of total fee). Default rate applies to all non-KOL referrers.\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:- [ ] Default referrer rate is 1000 bps of the total fee (configurable via environment/config) <!-- gap: no config env var REFERRAL_DEFAULT_RATE_BPS -->\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:  referrer_rate_bps         INTEGER NOT NULL,\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:-- KOL custom referrer rates (overrides default 1000 bps)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:2. If referrer exists → calculates `referrer_earned_lamports = fee_lamports × referrer_rate_bps / 10000` (where fee_lamports = wager_lamports × fee_bps / 10000)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:3. If not → use default rate from config/env (default: 1000 bps = 10% of total fee = 50 bps of wager)\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/300-referral-system/spec.md:- [ ] KOL custom rate is used when present, default rate otherwise <!-- gap: no rate lookup in settlement -->","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01RV1VboAcMDf4MT4RSfBWWe","session_id":"3e0bba06-3e2a-40d1-8fc4-6fd6659fa3ce","uuid":"34043e02-be9d-4146-b409-93de50146763","timestamp":"2026-03-25T11:47:01.712